name: Github-for-coco
body:
# **** Coco the cat needs a web page to track her various hourly mood changes.

9:00 PM - 6:00 AM - Night Patrol
6:15 AM - 7:00 PM - Sleep
7:05 PM - 7:10 PM - Eat
7:10 PM - 9:00 PM - Lick wash and annoy mood time.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
